OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FUnder 18s on the Isle of Man will be
OL,8,Fbanned from buying vape products -
OL,9,Fwith children no longer able to even
OL,10,Fsee them for sale, after new laws
OL,11,Fgained Royal Assent.
OL,13,FThe ban comes into force on from
OL,14,FMonday 27 May, as part of the Island's
OL,15,FVaping Products Act 2024, which also
OL,16,Flimits advertising of the products
OL,17,Ffrom 1 September.
