OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FMinister for the Cabinet Office, Kate
OL,8,FLord-Brennan MHK, who promoted the
OL,9,FBill, said: "The new Act will finally
OL,10,Falign us with the UK's age controls on
OL,11,Fthe sale of vaping products, and it
OL,12,Fwill surpass UK legislation by
OL,13,Fintroducing new point of sale
OL,14,Frestrictions, meaning that the display
OL,15,Fand marketing of vapes will be
OL,16,Frestricted in retailers accessible to
OL,17,Fchildren and young people.
OL,19,F"This is an important move for the
OL,20,Fcurrent and future health of young
OL,21,Fpeople."
