OL,4,Cthe sale and promotion of vaping
OL,5,Cproducts
OL,7,FAnyone who sells vaping products to a
OL,8,Fperson under the age of 18 could face
OL,9,Fa fine of #5,000, the government added.
OL,11,FIt wants retailers to start using the
OL,12,FChallenge 25 system for all sales of
OL,13,Fvapes - mirroring sales of alcohol and
OL,14,Ftobacco.
OL,16,FThe Bill was introduced following a
OL,17,Fstudy in the UK which suggested that
OL,18,Fvaping in young people is growing,
OL,19,Fwith 15.8% of 11`17-year-olds having
OL,20,Ftried vaping in 2022, a significant
OL,21,Fincrease compared to 3.8% in 2013.
