OL,7,FThe IOM Government said that while
OL,8,Fthere is no specific data for the
OL,9,Fisland, there has been an increase
OL,10,Freported locally of issues in schools
OL,11,Fand instances of petty theft from
OL,12,Fshops, which "suggest a rise in the
OL,13,Fuse of vaping products among young
OL,14,Fpeople" in the Island.
OL,16,FA Government statement added: "Further
OL,17,Fengagement with teenagers in the Isle
OL,18,Fof Man shows that we have a high
OL,19,Fprevalence of young people who vape.
